title: German Expressionist Christmas Pageant
description:
Written by Ryan Hunter
Starring: Jonathan Marballi, Jon Bershad, Kerry O'Brien, Lisa Kleinman, Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp, Zack Phillips, Alene Latimer, Kelly Hudson, Langan Kingsley, Kristy Lopez-Bernal

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, November 18, 2013.

Filmed by Matthew Alston and Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
